Package: morandipal
Title: Professional Morandi-Style Color Palettes for Single-Cell Visualization
Version: 1.0.2
Authors@R: 
    person("xiaoqqjun", 
           email = "xiaoqqjun@sina.com", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1813-1669"))
Description: A comprehensive R package providing 17 high-quality Morandi-style 
    color palettes optimized for single-cell RNA-seq data visualization. 
    Includes streamlined functions for UMAP/tSNE plotting with 
    customizable transparency, sizing, and clustering parameters.
